# Deploy Quality Gate (FleetFlow)

Applies when editing `deploy/` or running deploy commands. See also `pre-deploy-quality-gate.mdc` and `deploy/DEPLOY.md`.

## Hard blocker — run first

From `fleetflow---car-rental-&-finance-dashboard/`:

```bash
npm run test:all
```

Do not run remote deploy, `db:push`, or `users:push` until this exits `0`.

## Deploy scripts (project root)

| Command | Script | When |
|---------|--------|------|
| Remote full deploy | `node deploy/deploy-remote.mjs` | Code release to VPS |
| Rebuild on server | `node deploy/rebuild-app.mjs` | App-only rebuild |
| Sync users | `npm run users:push` | After auth/user env changes |
| Sync SQLite → PG | `npm run db:push` | After local data changes |
| PowerShell | `deploy/deploy-to-server.ps1` | Windows alternative to `deploy-remote.mjs` |

Requires `DEPLOY_SSH_PASSWORD` (or SSH keys). Credentials and SSH details: **`server-deployment.mdc`** (gitignored). Never commit `.env.deploy`, passwords, or `data/taxi.db`.

## Pre-deploy checklist

### Must do

- [ ] `npm run test:all` — calculations, filters, integration, fleet, oil-change, **vite build**
- [ ] Backup `data/taxi.db` before `db:push` or schema migrations
- [ ] If schema changed: run `npm run db:init` / `db:migrate` locally and verify integration tests
- [ ] Confirm `.env` / server `.env` has correct `POSTGRES_PASSWORD`, `API_PORT`, `VITE_API_URL`
- [ ] `npm run stop` (or stop Docker app) before deploy; restart after

### After deploy — verify on server

```bash
docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml ps
curl -s http://127.0.0.1/api/health
```

- [ ] Login works (`admin`, configured users)
- [ ] Garage → add car → tracking → refresh → data persists
- [ ] No secrets in git diff (`.env`, `.env.deploy`, DB files)

### Data push caution

- `db:push` **overwrites/migrates** production from local `data/taxi.db` — confirm backup and intent
- `users:push` syncs from `ENSURE_ADMIN` / `ENSURE_USERS` — rotate default passwords in production

## Security

- Change default demo passwords before public exposure
- Prefer SSH keys over root password; do not paste credentials into chat or commits
- Rotate credentials if leaked; see `deploy/DEPLOY.md` Security section

## Agent workflow

```
npm run test:all → backup DB → deploy-remote (or ps1) → health check → smoke test UI
```

If deploy script changes: document in `deploy/DEPLOY.md` and add integration coverage in `scripts/test-integration.mjs` when behavior is testable locally.
